OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FFerry passengers travelling through
OL,7,Fthe Port of Dover during the bank
OL,8,Fholiday getaway have been warned to
OL,9,Fexpect long queues and possible delays
OL,10,Famid EU border checks.
OL,12,FThe port is preparing for 18,000
OL,13,Ftravellers between Friday and Sunday,
OL,14,Fand warned that the busiest periods
OL,15,Feach day will be between 6am and about
OL,16,F1pm.
OL,18,FSaturday will be the port's busiest
OL,19,Fday of the year so far, with more than
OL,20,F8,000 travellers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
