OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FIn an advisory message, it said as
OL,7,Fthis is the first holiday period since
OL,8,Fthe implementation of the EU's entry-
OL,9,Fexit system (EES), officials are
OL,10,Furging passengers to follow travel
OL,11,Fadvice to keep journeys running
OL,12,Fsmoothly.
OL,14,FEES involves people from third-party
OL,15,Fcountries such as the UK having their
OL,16,Ffingerprints registered and photograph
OL,17,Ftaken to enter the Schengen Area,
OL,18,Fwhich consists of 29 European
OL,19,Fcountries, mainly in the EU.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FBut the Port of Dover said the full
OL,7,Fsystem was not running for cars yet,
OL,8,Fand that it is still awaiting delivery
OL,9,Fand installation of the French
OL,10,Ftechnology.
OL,12,FIt means French border police are
OL,13,Fmanually creating traveller records at
OL,14,Fthe eastern docks.
OL,16,FThe Port of Dover said there were hour-
OL,17,Flong processing waits at border
OL,18,Fcontrol by 6am on Friday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
