OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FPassengers are being advised to use
OL,7,Fthe main road routes to the port,
OL,8,Farrive no earlier than two hours
OL,9,Fbefore departure and ensure they have
OL,10,Fa confirmed booking and all travel
OL,11,Fdocuments ready.
OL,13,FTravellers are also being told to
OL,14,Fprepare for possible delays by
OL,15,Fbringing food and water, while anyone
OL,16,Fwho misses their ferry because of
OL,17,Fdisruption will be moved on to the
OL,18,Fnext available sailing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
