OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the AA has estimated that
OL,7,F23.4 million car journeys will take
OL,8,Fplace on Friday.
OL,10,FIt highlighted likely traffic
OL,11,Fblackspots to include routes heading
OL,12,Ftowards east coast destinations such
OL,13,Fas Skegness, the M4 from London
OL,14,Ftowards Wales, and the M6 towards the
OL,15,Fnorth-west coast.
OL,17,FThe RAC expects leisure traffic to
OL,18,Fpeak on Friday and Saturday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
