PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FStrike action and engineering work
OL,7,Fwill cause disruption on a number of
OL,8,Froutes on Britain's railways.
OL,10,FWalkouts by members of the Transport
OL,11,FSalaried Staffs' Association on Friday
OL,12,Fand Saturday in a dispute over pay
OL,13,Fwill affect West Midlands Railway
OL,14,F(WMR) and London Northwestern Railway
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FTimetables will be slashed on both
OL,18,Fdays, including no WMT trains after
OL,19,F7pm on Friday or before 7am on
OL,20,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
