OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FNetwork Rail engineering work means
OL,7,Fparts of key intercity lines will be
OL,8,Fshut.
OL,10,FThe East Coast Main Line will be
OL,11,Fclosed between York and Darlington
OL,12,Ffrom Saturday through to Monday.
OL,14,FBuses will replace trains between
OL,15,FNewport and Bristol Parkway from
OL,16,FSaturday for two weeks.
OL,18,FThere will be no Thameslink services
OL,19,Fthrough central London between
OL,20,FSaturday and Monday, affecting
OL,21,Fservices to Gatwick and Luton airports.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
