PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FTravel trade organisation Abta said
OL,7,Fthere will be a surge in families
OL,8,Fheading off on holiday this weekend as
OL,9,Fit marks the start of half-term breaks
OL,10,Ffor many schools.
OL,12,FIt reported strong demand for short-
OL,13,Fhaul sunshine holidays in destinations
OL,14,Fsuch as mainland Spain, Italy, the
OL,15,FBalearic and Canary Islands, and
OL,16,FPortugal, as well as city breaks in
OL,17,FMilan, Nice and Barcelona.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
