PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779538271
OL,3,CFerry passengers told to prepare for
OL,4,Clong queues and delays at Port of Dover
OL,6,FMeanwhile, parking app company RingGo
OL,7,Fsaid its analysis of recent bank
OL,8,Fholiday periods found Saturday is
OL,9,Flikely to be the busiest day of the
OL,10,Flong weekend at coastal towns and
OL,11,Fcities such as Bournemouth, Hastings
OL,12,Fand Torquay.
OL,14,FIt said seaside towns are
OL,15,F"consistently outperforming inland
OL,16,Flocations" during bank holidays in
OL,17,Fterms of the number of parking
OL,18,Fsessions recorded.
OL,20,FThe Met Office has forecast a heatwave
OL,21,Fin some parts this weekend.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
